  <brief_title>Surgical Versus Conservative Treatment of Acute Mallet Fingers; a Randomised Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Surgical Versus Conservative Treatment of Acute Mallet Fingers; a Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
